StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetDataSheetStartPool]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@OrgID int , @FiscalYear int
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT CONTRACT_ID, COMPONENT_CODE, GENDER_CODE, TargetMonth FROM [USMC].[GetDataSheetEndMonthPoolByMonth] (@OrgID, @FiscalYear-1, 9)
END
